{"route":{"route":"/posts/ce6c7d90/","outputPath":"posts/ce6c7d90/index.html","kind":"post","title":"秘密共享","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"ce6c7d90"}},"description":"拉格朗日插值法 对某个多项式函数，已知有给定的k + 1个取值点：(x0,y0)...(xk,yk) 假设任意两个不同的xj都互不相同，那么应用拉格朗日插值公式所得到的拉格朗日插值多项式为： f(x) = l0+l1...+lk即可求出多项式 example Shamir 秘密共享 生成 设需要生成w个密钥，至少需要t","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/秘密共享.md","route":"/posts/ce6c7d90/","abbrlink":"ce6c7d90","title":"秘密共享","date":"2022-10-10 11:05:22","updated":"2022-10-10 11:05:22","tags":["Crypto","Shamir"],"categories":["Crypto"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<h2 id=\"拉格朗日插值法\">拉格朗日插值法</h2>\n<p>对某个多项式函数，已知有给定的k + 1个取值点：<code>(x0,y0)...(xk,yk)</code><br>\n假设任意两个不同的xj都互不相同，那么应用拉格朗日插值公式所得到的拉格朗日插值多项式为：</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l0 = (((x-x1)(x-x2)...(x-xk))/((x0-x1)(x0-x2)...(x0-xk)))<span class=\"hljs-emphasis\">*y0</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-emphasis\">    ...</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-emphasis\">lk = ...</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-emphasis\"></span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><code>f(x) = l0+l1...+lk</code>即可求出多项式</p>\n<h3 id=\"example\">example</h3>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">已知3个点(4,10)(5,5.25)(6,1)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l0 = (((x-5)(x-6))/((4-5)(4-6))) * 10</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l1 = (((x-4)(x-6))/((5-4)(5-6))) * 5.25</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l2 = (((x-4)(x-5))/((6-4)(6-5))) * 1</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">f(x) = l0+l1+l2 = 1/4(x^2-28x+136)</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"shamir-秘密共享\">Shamir 秘密共享</h2>\n<p>生成</p>\n<ul>\n<li>设需要生成w个密钥，至少需要t个密钥才能算出真实密钥</li>\n<li>选择一个数P，之后所有数都需要进行模运算</li>\n<li>设置真实密钥K</li>\n<li>随机选择t-1个不大于P的数 <code>a0,a1...at-1</code></li>\n<li>得到多项式 <code>f(x)=K+a0x+a1x^2...+at-1x^t</code></li>\n<li>将<code>x=1.x=2...x=w</code>带入多项式即可获得多个密钥<code>(1,k1)(2,k2)...(w,kw)</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>解密</p>\n<ul>\n<li>利用拉格朗日插值法即可算出多项式</li>\n<li>需要带上模计算多项式，如果计算多项式时有除法需要进行计算模乘逆元</li>\n<li>因为只需要K所以计算的时候可以直接x=0</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"eg1\">eg1</h3>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-txt\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">w=4,t=3,K=2,p=23，选择随机数 a0=3, a1=2</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">加密</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">得到多项式 f(x) = (2 + 3x + 2x^2) mod 23</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">f(1) = 2, f(2) = 16, f(3) = 6, f(4) = 0</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">获得4个密钥(1,2)(2,16)(3,6)(4,0)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">解密</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">选择其中三个进行解密，(1,7)(3,6)(4,0)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l0 = (((x-3)(x-4))/((1-3)(1-4)))*7</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l1 = (((x-1)(x-4))/((3-1)(3-4)))*6</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l2 = (((x-1)(x-3))/((4-1)(4-3)))*0</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">将x=0带入可得</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l0 = 14</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">20</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l1 = -12</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">21</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l2 = 0</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">22</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">23</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">可得k = (l0+l1+l2) mod 23</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">24</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">     = 2 mod 23</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">25</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">     = 2</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"eg2\">eg2</h3>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-txt\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">w=5,t=3,k=13,p=17,选择随机数a0=10,a1=2</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">加密</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">得到多项式 f(x) = (13 + 10x + 2x^2) mod 17</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">f(1) = 8, f(2) = 7, f(3) = 10, f(4) = 0, f(5) = 11</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">获得5个密钥(1,8)(2,7)(3,10)(4,0)(5,11)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">解密</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">选择其中三个进行解密，(1,8)(2,7)(5,11)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l0 = 11 * ( ((x-1)(x-2)) / ((5-1)(5-2)) )</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l1 = 7  * ( ((x-1)(x-5)) / ((2-1)(2-5)) )</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l2 = 8  * ( ((x-2)(x-5)) / ((1-2)(1-5)) )</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">将 x=0 带入</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l0 = 22/12</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">20</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l1 = -140/12</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">21</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">l2 = 240/12</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">22</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">23</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">K = (l0+l1+l2) mod 17</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">24</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  = (61/6) mod 17</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">25</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  = (61 * 6^-1) mod 17 // 6^-1为6关于17的模乘逆元为3</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">26</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  = (61 * 3) mod 17 </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">27</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  = 13</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"中国剩余定理\">中国剩余定理</h2>\n<p>example</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-txt\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">w=5,t=3,K=117</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">选择w个d,要求单调递增并两两互素,t个最小的d相乘大于K,K大于t-1个最大d相乘</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">d1=4,d2=5,d3=7,d4=9,d5=11</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">计算 ki=Key mod di // = -&gt; \\equal</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">k1 = 117 mod 4 = 1</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">k2 = 117 mod 5 = 2</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">k3 = 117 mod 7 = 5</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">k4 = 117 mod 9 = 0</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">k5 = 117 mod 11 = 7</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">即五个密钥(1,4),(2,5),(3,7),(0,9),(7,11)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">解密</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">选其中三个密钥(1,4)(2,5)(3,7)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">可得</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">20</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">k mod 4 = 1</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">21</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">k mod 5 = 2</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">22</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">k mod 11 = 7</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">23</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">24</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">分解为</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">25</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">k1 mod 4 = 1, k1 mod 5 = 0, k1 mod 11 = 0</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">26</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; 5 * 11 * x1 mod 4 = 1</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">27</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; x1 = 3</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">28</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; k1 = 55 * 3 = 165</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">29</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">30</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">k2 mod 4 = 0, k2 mod 5 = 2, k2 mod 11 = 0</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">31</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; 4 * 11 * x2 mod 5 = 2</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">32</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; 44 * x2 * 2^-1 mod 5 = 1 // 2^-1 为2关于5的模乘逆元</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">33</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; 44 * x2 * 3 mod 5 = 1</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">34</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; 132 * x2 mod 5 = 1 // 相当于算132关于5的模乘逆元</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">35</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; x2 = 3</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">36</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; k2 = 44 * 3 = 132</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">37</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">38</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">k3 mod 4 = 0, k3 mod 5 = 0, k3 mod 11 = 7</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">39</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; 4 * 5 * x3 mod 11 = 7</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">40</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; 20 * x3 * 7^-1 mod 11 = 1 // 7^-1 为7关于11的模乘逆元</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">41</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; 20 * x3 * 8 mod 11 = 1</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">42</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; 160 * x3 mod 11 = 1 // 相当于算160关于11的模乘逆元</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">43</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; x3 = 2</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">44</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; k3 = 40</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">45</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">46</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">K = (k1 + k2 + k3) mod 4*5*11</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">47</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  = (165+132+40) mod 220</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">48</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  = 337 mod 220</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">49</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  = 117</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">50</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">51</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">另一种：</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">52</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">k1 mod 4 = 1, k1 mod 5 = 0, k1 mod 11 = 0</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">53</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; 1 * (k1 mod 4 = 1, k1 mod 5 = 0, k1 mod 11 = 0) </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">54</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; 5 * 11 * x1 mod 4 = 1</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">55</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; x1 = 3</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">56</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; k1 = 1 * 55 * 3 = 165</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">57</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">58</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">k2 mod 4 = 0, k2 mod 5 = 2, k2 mod 11 = 0</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">59</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; 2 * (k2 mod 4 = 0, k2 mod 5 = 1, k2 mod 11 = 0)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">60</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; 4 * 11 * x2 mod 5 = 1</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">61</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; x2 = 4</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">62</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; k2 2 * 44 * 4 = 352</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">63</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">64</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">k3 mod 4 = 0, k3 mod 5 = 0, k3 mod 11 = 7</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">65</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; 7 * (k3 mod 4 = 0, k3 mod 5 = 0, k3 mod 11 = 1)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">66</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; 4 * 5 * x3 mod 11 = 1</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">67</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; x3 = 5</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">68</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  -&gt; k3 = 7 * 20 * 5 = 700</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">69</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">70</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">K = (k1 + k2 + k3) mod (4*5*11)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">71</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  = (165 + 352 + 700) mod 220</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">72</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  = 1217 mod 220</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">73</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  = 117</span></span></code></pre>\n<hr>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shamir%27s_Secret_Sharing\">Shamir’s Secret Sharing - Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%8B%89%E6%A0%BC%E6%9C%97%E6%97%A5%E6%8F%92%E5%80%BC%E6%B3%95\">拉格朗日插值法 - Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/95362628\">趣说密码学（五）秘密共享方案——shamir,中国剩余定理,Brickell和Blakley</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/pyrie/p/sss_py.html\">Shamir秘密共享方案 (Python)</a></li>\n</ul>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[{"id":"拉格朗日插值法","text":"拉格朗日插值法","level":2},{"id":"example","text":"example","level":3},{"id":"shamir-秘密共享","text":"Shamir 秘密共享","level":2},{"id":"eg1","text":"eg1","level":3},{"id":"eg2","text":"eg2","level":3},{"id":"中国剩余定理","text":"中国剩余定理","level":2}],"slugForSearch":"ce6c7d90","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}